*Ostalo* je još dosta da se uradi. (There is still a lot to do.)

*Ostalo* je nekoliko stvari koje treba da odradim. (There are still a few things I need to do.)

Dok sam *ostalo* pričao sa njim, nisam ni primetio da je otišao. (While I was still talking to him, I didn't even notice he had gone.)

Ostalo je nekoliko sati do ponoći. (There are still a few hours until midnight.)

Od *ostalog* novca kupio je sve što mu je trebalo. (He bought everything he needed with the rest of the money.)